{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.960", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.320", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.720", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mein Vorredner Herr Stracke von der CSU hat es zu Beginn der Debatte gesagt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.040", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Uns geht es in erster Linie um die Frage, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.960", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie man aus der Armut herauskommen kann. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.960", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr uns hei\u00dft das: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.600", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Perspektiven schaffen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.600", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Weg geht \u00fcber den Arbeitsmarkt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.800", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist wichtig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.880", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Arbeit zu schaffen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.680", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In dieser Hinsicht ist tats\u00e4chlich viel gelungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.480", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das hei\u00dft aber nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.040", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir prinzipiell leugnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.240", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es an der einen oder anderen Stelle Armut in Deutschland gibt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.760", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich m\u00f6chte an dieser Stelle einige sehr pers\u00f6nliche Gedanken formulieren; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.800", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn meine Pr\u00e4gung steht mit Armut\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.640", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zumindest mit der, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.200", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00fcber die wir hier reden\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.240", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den entsprechenden Instrumenten und Begriffen wie \u201erelative Armut\u201c und \u201eArmutsgef\u00e4hrdung\u201c in Verbindung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.240", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich selber h\u00e4tte nach dieser Statistik mit meiner Familie zu 50\u00a0Prozent meiner Lebenszeit unter dieser Grenze gelegen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.920", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das war mir in diesem Zeitraum nie bewusst. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.920", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich w\u00fcrde mich auch nachtr\u00e4glich nicht als arm bezeichnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.680", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit leugne ich nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.640", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass das statistisch so war; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.200", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber es geht dabei um mehr Elemente als die finanzielle Ausstattung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.360", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist nicht leicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "78.960", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "davon zu leben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "78.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.880", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber m\u00f6glich."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.200", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sp\u00e4ter wurde ich\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.600", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das hat vielleicht auch mit dieser Erfahrung zu tun\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.080", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Heilsarmeeoffizier. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.760", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Erst habe ich in der Heilsarmee als Sozialarbeiter gearbeitet und sp\u00e4ter bei der Heilsarmee die Ausbildung zum Theologen gemacht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.320", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In diesem Umfeld habe ich mich nat\u00fcrlich in erster Linie um diese Menschen in unserer Gesellschaft gek\u00fcmmert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "100.800", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich habe in diesem Umfeld unter anderem zwei Tafeln gegr\u00fcndet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "100.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "103.520", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "An dieser Stelle muss ich zu der ganzen Debatte \u00fcber die Tafeln sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "103.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.440", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Den Zulauf bei den Tafeln und das Manko der Tafeln, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "109.680", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht genug zum Verteilen zu haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "109.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.880", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "als Messinstrument f\u00fcr Armut in Deutschland zu nehmen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.760", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "halte ich f\u00fcr ziemlich haneb\u00fcchen;"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "119.320", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn die Tafeln sind im Angesicht des \u00dcberflusses gegr\u00fcndet worden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "119.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.400", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dieser \u00dcberfluss sollte denjenigen in unserer Gesellschaft zugutekommen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "124.240", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die weniger haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "124.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.200", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Situation der Tafeln kann nur ein Indiz daf\u00fcr sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "131.200", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie es um die Armut in Deutschland bestellt ist; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "131.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "133.320", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber einen Antrag darauf aufzubauen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "133.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "135.720", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie beziehen sich ja an mehreren Stellen auf die Tafeln\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "135.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "138.320", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "halte ich f\u00fcr \u00e4u\u00dferst schwierig."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "138.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.040", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sollten tats\u00e4chlich \u00fcber die statistischen Instrumente diskutieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.000", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie Herr Strengmann-Kuhn es gesagt hat. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "149.640", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Welche nehmen wir? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "149.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.000", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.040", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die wir in diesem Bereich arbeiten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.000", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wissen alle: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "157.240", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn wir jedem in Deutschland 100\u00a0Euro mehr geben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "157.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.680", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "haben wir danach gleich viel Arme in Deutschland."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.280", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nach dieser mathematischen Berechnung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.480", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die von 60\u00a0Prozent bzw. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "169.240", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "50\u00a0Prozent ausgeht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "169.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "172.200", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "haben wir relativ gesehen gleich viel Armut in Deutschland."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "172.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.080", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ein letzter Gedanke zu dem Ziel Ihres Antrags\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.120", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich habe mich mit dem Antrag besch\u00e4ftigt; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "179.600", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das war ja auch meine Aufgabe\u00a0\u2013: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "179.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "180.640", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Unterstellen wir einmal, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "180.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "182.200", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es Ihnen wirklich um die Kinder, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "182.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "182.960", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Alleinerziehenden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "182.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.480", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die \u00e4lteren Menschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "188.000", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Menschen mit Behinderungen und die Langzeitarbeitslosen geht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "188.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.120", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die tats\u00e4chlich und nicht nur laut dieser Statistik in Armut sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.760", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das sind m\u00f6glicherweise 20\u00a0Prozent\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.480", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das ist jetzt eine aus der Luft gegriffene Zahl\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.080", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "von denen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.760", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die generell nach dieser Statistik arm sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.520", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Ziel, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "203.280", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Menschen generell aus Armut zu befreien, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "203.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.120", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "teilen wir; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.520", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber wir kommen zu anderen Schl\u00fcssen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.720", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen auf andere Weise Perspektiven schaffen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.680", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zum Beispiel, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.080", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "indem wir \u00a7\u00a016h SGB\u00a0II so formulieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.720", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass junge Leute aus dem ALG\u2011II-Bezug herausgef\u00fchrt werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "219.000", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das wollen wir ganz konkret f\u00fcr eine Personengruppe formulieren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "219.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "220.800", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Rechnen wir Ihre Forderungen einmal durch: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "220.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "223.280", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn wir tats\u00e4chlich Ihre Forderungen umsetzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "223.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "224.520", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann werden wir\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "224.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.040", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "jemand sprach vorhin von dem Preis, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "230.400", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den man daf\u00fcr zahlen muss\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "230.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.080", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "f\u00fcr die 20\u00a0Prozent, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.080", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die wirklich Hilfe brauchen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "238.840", 
   "id": "s000089", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die auf gut Deutsch tats\u00e4chlich in der Schei\u00dfe sitzen,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "238.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "241.600", 
   "id": "s000090", 
